01

13 New cases reported outside Hubei

The 16th, January twenty-three.

Wind and snow blew away the dark clouds, Wuhan is a clear sky.

A total of 2,048 new confirmed cases and 1,563 suspected cases were reported nationwide on May 16. There were 105 new deaths (100 in Hubei, 3 in Henan and 2 in Guangdong) .

As of June 16, there were 57,934 confirmed cases (including 10,644 serious cases) , 10,844 cured cases, 1770 dead cases, 70,548 confirmed cases and 7264 suspected cases.

There were 1,933 new confirmed cases in Hubei (1,690 in Wuhan) , 1,016 new cured cases (543 in Wuhan) and 100 new deaths (76 in Wuhan, a sharp drop from 110 in Wuhan on the 15th) .

There were 6639 cured cases (3458 in Wuhan) and 1696 died cases (1309 in Wuhan) .

The good news is that 13 new cases have been confirmed outside Hubei.

A total of 115 new confirmed cases were reported in areas other than Hubei in China on June 16. In the past 13 days, there were 890 cases with 3 days, 731 cases with 4 days, 707 cases with 5 days, 696 cases with 6 days and 558 cases with 7 days, 509 cases were 8 days, 444 cases 9 days, 381 cases 10 days, 377 cases 11 days, 312 cases 12 days, 267 cases 13 days, 22114 days, 16615 days.

I hope to break 100 tomorrow.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
I think there should be two inflection points, one is the medical inflection point, the other is the social control inflection point. Put simply, there are inflection points inside and outside the hospital.

Has the medical inflection point come yet? Only the hospital director has a say in this.

Wang Xinghuan, director of Wuhan Raytheon Mountain Hospital, said: The real inflection point has come, and now a lot of consumption inside are stocks. In terms of new cases, I've observed a decrease in the number of fevers over the last five days. It is a slope, gradually falling, steadily falling, no rebound, I am very confident.

There you go.

What's GonNa Happen in the next few days?

The overall trend of the epidemic in Hubei Province is good, and the forecast curves of Xiaogan, Ezhou and Qianjiang suggest a strong warning signal, said the Public Security Emergency Response Team of Tsinghua University on Monday

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
They believe the number of new cases in Wuhan will also decline.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
At this point, big data speculation is essential.

In addition to the team from Tsinghua University, I think the Shaanxi Provincial Bureau of Statistics is doing a good job. The number of patients in Shaanxi and its surrounding provinces was forecasted.

I have been wondering, these study statistics undergraduate students, master's degree students, doctoral students why not go to the Bureau of Statistics? I asked the teachers of Statistics Department, they mostly go to securities companies, large companies, research institutes and other higher-income units.

I keep calling for statistics students to work in statistics. Only in this way can we improve the research level of statistical cadres.

There's one more piece of data worth analyzing.

At present, China has about 270 million students in school, and efforts to achieve "suspension without suspension. ". Some say this is an opportunity for an explosion of online education in the country.

The real explosion of online education began around 2010.

From 2012 to 2018, online education gradually matured, the size of the market expanded four times, the market size of more than 300 billion yuan.

However, in sharp contrast to the prosperity of the industry, most of the companies in this industry are not "moist" , or even a bit miserable, because the ability to make money is not enough, the ability to spend money is very fierce.

Is this an opportunity to explode?

02

Wuhan puts forward the "five hundred percent" goal

All village groups, communities, subdivisions and residential areas in urban and rural areas will be subject to the strictest 24 hour closed management, the Government of the People's Republic of China announced Sunday.

For example, all non-essential public places will be closed and all mass activities will cease. The community (village) , community, residential area, building, workplace and other grass-roots units with newly diagnosed (including clinically diagnosed) cases of coronary pneumonia should be closed and hard isolated for 14 days. We will strengthen the protection of residents'daily necessities and promote online group purchases in residential areas (village groups) .

All residents of the dynamic rolling screen network, so that "do not leave a door, do not fall a person, constantly one day, " to ensure full coverage, no blind area. If they refuse to cooperate, the Public Security Bureau shall take compulsory measures according to law.

This is supposed to be the strictest in the country. But it wasn't the first.

At noon on the 16th, a friend sent pictures in the Fruit Lake pedestrian street, pedestrians or many.

As early as ten days ago, some netizens suggested that Wuhan should implement "military control" . That's pretty much how it is now. Some of the videos show people walking down the street without masks, clashing with police, who unhesitatingly handcuff them away.

On the basis of the unified regulations of the whole province, what about the situation in Wuhan?

Wuhan's new crown pneumonia epidemic prevention and control headquarters held a video conference on the 16th, the deployment of a three-day central dragnet-style investigation, resolutely contain the spread of the epidemic. Wang Zhonglin, a member of the Standing Committee of the Hubei Provincial Party Committee and Party secretary of the Wuhan Municipal Party Committee, said that there was no way out of the The Parting of the Ways. We must win.

Wuhan has launched a three-day centralized network-type large-scale investigation to find out the bottom figure and push forward the implementation of the "five percent 100 percent" work target, that is, "100 percent of confirmed patients should be collected, 100 percent of suspected patients nucleic acid testing, 100 percent of fever patients tested, 100 percent of close contacts isolated, 100 percent of residential villages under 24-hour closed management. "

Wang Zhonglin stressed that in the process of carrying out a large-scale centralized investigation, those who do not obey the closed management of the residential area should be dealt with seriously and exposed in accordance with the law; all districts should improve the material distribution system in a timely manner, we need to organize all efforts to speed up nucleic acid testing, to screen suspected patients with fever at home as soon as possible, and to protect community workers, said O.

In addition, the Wuhan New Crown Pneumonia Epidemic Prevention and control headquarters issued a notice on strict public places epidemic prevention and control measures (No. 13) .

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Two things stand out.

Must be open to the implementation of public scanning code access management. The management units of hotels, hotels, supermarkets, agricultural markets and other places with high density of people shall establish a daily health monitoring system. Those entering shall take body temperature, wear masks and keep a certain distance. Those who do not wear masks are not allowed to enter. Once found abnormal body temperature should be sent to the fever clinic, and do a good job in registration, information report, environmental disinfection and other prevention and control work.

We will implement a registration system for the purchase of medicines by retail pharmacies. People who buy medicines such as cough and fever must fill in information such as ID card number, personal contact information, emergency contact information, detailed residential address, etc. . Pharmacies should register and report.

I don't know why I can still buy cough medicine, the other local rules, pharmacies do not buy cough medicine, can only go directly to the hospital.

In response to the problem of vegetable supply in the city centre, Wuhan has taken the initiative of providing counterpart support to the city centre in Xincheng. Xinzhou District counterpart support Wuchang District, Qingshan District, Wuhan and East Lake; Jiangxia District counterpart Support Hongshan District and Donghu New Technology Development Zone; Huangpi District counterpart support Jiang'an District and Jiang'an District; Dongxihu counterpart Support Qiao Estuary; Caidian District counterpart to Hanyang District.

This reflects the cooperation between the central city and the new (far) city. When others come to help us, we must help ourselves.

03

What is a negative-pressure car?

In the epidemic prevention and control, everyone is learning and popularizing science.

On the 13th, the first batch of 72 negative pressure ambulances produced by Jiangling Automobile Group Company arrived in Han.

At 9:30 on the 16th, 72 negative-pressure ambulances made by Xiamen Jinlong Automobile Group Co. and donated by caring enterprises and organizations passed through 95,014 special freight trains of China Railway at Wuhan Dahualing Railway Logistics Base, from Xiamen Haicang's international logistics port, the whole journey is 1318 kilometers.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
At 11:30 am on the 16th, 13 large flatbed vehicles carrying 40 negative-pressure ambulances, which were escorted by relays from five provinces and cities including Hubei, Henan, Hebei, Tianjin and Liaoning, successfully arrived at the Nangang Gas Station of Sinopec in Caidian District, Wuhan, and in the same day sent to Ezhou, Xiaogan, Huanggang, and other 38 hospitals.

The 40 cars were built by Brilliance Renault Gold Cup and purchased and donated by Midea Group.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The transport of these vehicles is also not easy due to climatic factors.

On the 14th, 13 flatcars set off from Shenyang. That night, heavy snow in Tianjin, Highway Control, the motorcade stranded in Tianjin Highway Shuangjie Station Service area.

The traffic team of the new pneumonia prevention and control headquarters in Hubei Province immediately contacted the Tianjin authorities. The Tianjin traffic and public security departments took immediate action and arranged for police cars and road administration vehicles to escort them all the way out of Tianjin.

At about 20:30, the drivers had eaten all the instant noodles, bread and so on, and the motorcade entered the Hengshui Service area of Hebei Expressway for a rest. The person in charge of Hebei Province Road Transport Bureau calls on his own initiative, and contacted the Public Security Department to give all support to the team. At about 7:00 on the 15th, under the escort of Hebei Traffic Police, the motorcade started on time in the rain and snow.

The Hubei Provincial Transportation Department then urgently contacted the Henan Provincial Transportation Department. Transport authorities in Henan Province have prepared lunch boxes, instant noodles and hot water in Xinyang and other service areas along the route to ensure that lunch and dinner are available, and have sent police cars and road administration vehicles to escort them along the route.

On the 16th, the convoy entered Hubei Province, where it was escorted by the Jingzhu Road Administration and traffic police, and arrived at the BeijingHong KongMacau Expressway at 10 am.

These are touching stories.

A negative-pressure ambulance, known as a "flowing N95 mask, " has a lower air pressure inside the vehicle than outside, which locks the virus carried by the patient inside the vehicle and highly filters it as it discharges air, to ensure that the ambulance on the road itself does not become a source of pollution, is the new pneumonia transferred to patients with the main means of transport and the battle of "epidemic" an important line of defense.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
With the delivery of the Vulcan Mountain Hospital, a large number of just produced the negative pressure ambulance to Wuhan in succession. Production of negative-pressure ambulance companies including Beijing Automobile Futian, Saic Chase, Jiangling Ford, Fujian Benz, Brilliance Gold Cup, Chery River, Yutong and so on.

On the 16th, from Chen Jiji Hongqiao industrial park heard a roar of machinery, a large transport vehicle is loaded with a variety of building materials, filed into the park one after another. Workers in White, yellow and red hard hats are busy shuttling around the construction site of the Yangtze River New Town Shelter Hospital.

There's a 72-hour battle going on..

In accordance with the Wuhan Municipal Party Committee's requirement of "strengthening patient care as the top priority, continue to build a new 'shelter hospital' , do a good job in advance, and strive for the 'bed and other people' " for the prevention and control of epidemic situations, the Jiang'an District government decided Wednesday to open a large shelter hospital in the Yangtze River New town.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The Yangtze New City Shelter Hospital plans to build 20 cabins, each with 1,188 square meters and a total capacity of more than 3,000 beds, making it Wuhan's largest shelter hospital by far.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Different from the temporary movable board building adopted by Huoshenshan and Leishenshan hospitals, the new town of Yangtze River Shelter Hospital is reconstructed from the original temporary factory building.

Wuhan is urgent, all sides support. At present, the medical support teams from all over the country are still gathering and going to Wuhan one after another for first-line support.

In the middle of these professional teams, there are a number of fast-running figure, they are civil rescue team, most of the material as a "carrier" role, between the outskirts of Wuhan and the city center.

The WEY Home Guard, organized by Zhang Fan, is part of the Wey Home Guard, a group of more than 200 people who are selfless and do not fear death.

The team consisted of 273 private cars, with nearly 100 people assigned directly to the convoy of medical personnel, with the remainder dedicated to the transportation and delivery of assigned tasks.

They also often come across more painful things, such as many people well-intentioned donations, but supplies do not meet medical needs, or even by middlemen "cheat" , "pit.

Through the online procurement of more than 9000 sets of protective clothing, online payment, the middleman "shoddy" delivery to Wuhan surrounding, team members in hand-over inspection only to find that "was pit.

04

Things Beyond Wuhan

Huanggang issued a circular on the 16th: Active Treatment for fever cough, prevention and control personnel screening found new fever personnel and organization of medical treatment, the public found new fever personnel reported once verified, a one-off bonus of 500 yuan.

The other day, Fang County took the same approach. After fever, oneself see a doctor, can get 1000 yuan reward. Finders will be awarded $500. Over 100 cases in two days. And now Huanggang is using it.

Misreporting body temperature, coming from Wuhan, etc. , is a crime of obstructing the prevention and treatment of infectious diseases. A lot of people probably didn't know it was that bad.

On January 22, Anhui Public official Wang drove his car to Suzhou, Anhui East high-speed Railway Station to pick up his eldest daughter Wang, who was returning home from Wuhan.

February 5, the community staff visited the investigation found Wang a history of returning home in Wuhan, Wang still did not report the situation.

His wife, surnamed Chang, and his youngest daughter, COVID-19, were reported to have returned home on February 8 after they developed suspected symptoms of infection on February 2 and February 7.

After her daughter returned home in Wuhan, she went out many times to have dinner with relatives, classmates, party, shopping, on duty, participate in epidemic prevention work, and illegally transacted vehicle passes to take her and her daughter to the hospital for treatment.

On February 9 and 10, Wang's wife, Chang, and his youngest daughter, Wang, were diagnosed with new pneumonia. As a result, more than 1,700 residents in the district were isolated at home, and the hospital was forced to implement a closed management. According to preliminary statistics, more than 400 people were in close contact, causing serious consequences during the epidemic prevention and control.

On February 10, the Si County Public Security Bureau opened a case against Wang for alleged negligence and dangerous methods of endangering public security. The SI County procuratorate coordinates with the county public security bureau, and intervenes in the investigation in advance according to the law. After giving opinions on the collection, fixation and improvement of the evidence in the case, it guides the Public Security Bureau to change the nature of the case, further investigation on suspicion of obstructing the prevention and treatment of infectious diseases. As a result of Wang was diagnosed as new pneumonia asymptomatic infection, February 11, public security organs on suspicion of obstruction of infectious disease prevention and treatment of Wang obtained bail pending trial.

This is no laughing matter.

Nanjing municipal government, from the 16th by bus, subway, the need to scan posted in the car Qr code for registration. If you do not carry a smartphone or do not know how to operate the passenger, the operator or other passengers can be tied to their mobile phone number, complete the information registration. In addition, Suzhou also announced that on the basis of the full implementation of taxi passenger registration, the real name registration of bus passengers will be further implemented from today.

Closed Communities, community management personnel and access to the owners, unavoidable contact, will not be infected? People think of Wechat.

One of my elementary school classmates in Wuyishan, Fujian Province, told me about something they were doing in Henan Province.

In Zhumadian, 14, the BeijingHong KongMacau Expressway Changzhuang town epidemic monitoring points and hope Avenue Changzhuang town epidemic monitoring points officially launched scanning Qr code to register personal information.

With the help of the company concerned, the Changzhuang town government has developed a two-dimensional code for the registration of highway checkpoints, and standardized the "information registration form for entry and exit checkpoints" , set the license plate number, driver information, whether there is a fever, Hubei travel history, with the car personnel information and other mandatory content. The card-point staff posted the Qr code to a clear location at the check point. While waiting for the temperature to be measured at the card point, vehicles on and off the highway directly scanned the Qr Code in the hands of the staff with their mobile phones, according to the relevant requirements to fill in the information submitted to achieve rapid detection through the whole process of only one or two minutes.

Scanning Qr Code Registration Personnel Information effectively avoids the risk of cross-infection in the process of hand-passing pen and paper between staff and crew.

A few days ago, some community cadres in Wuhan told me about this problem. The most dangerous thing is that the community cadres register the people and vehicles going in and out.

So Zhumadian's approach is worth promoting.

Academic concerns about the nation's economy

Economic data from the Psycho.

The current economic data are, in part, bad, as the Psycho puts it.

The average daily coal consumption of the six power generation groups dropped from more than 700,000 tonnes a day in December to 372,000 tonnes a day on February 11, a drop of nearly 50 per cent and about 40 per cent compared with the same period last year. All kinds of problems caused by the shutdown of enterprises.

From Dec. 31 to Feb. 11, the floor space for commercial housing transactions in 30 cities was only 5.04 Manpei, down about 90 percent from the same period last year. I can't go to the sales department.

But evergrande in online sales, the effect is good.

At 9:00 am on the 16th, Evergrande Group held a "full implementation of online sales" press conference by means of online video, revealing the performance of online sales for the first time.

Evergrande implementation of a comprehensive "online purchase" only 3 days, the growth momentum of sales data rapidly Mengmeng. At present, customers through the online purchase of 47,540 units, a total value of about 58 billion yuan, the largest subscription of a property up to 870 units. It was unexpected.

From the first day of the Lunar New Year to February 11, China sent only 234 million passengers by various means of transport, down about 80 percent compared with the same period last year. Even first-tier cities with the highest concentration of return trips after the holiday have seen declines of about 70 percent compared with the same period last year in Beijing, about 65 percent in Shanghai, about 74 percent in Guangzhou and about 70 percent in Shenzhen. 20 billion yuan in airline refunds.

Passenger car sales were down 21.5 per cent from a year earlier to 1.699 M in January, and are expected to double in February.

China's express delivery business dropped 95 per cent year-on-year during the Lunar New Year holiday and is expected to remain down about 20 per cent year-on-year in February once construction starts.

In the context of the nationwide "city closure" , all kinds of catering, hotel and tourism services have in fact come to a complete standstill, operating rate will not exceed 1% , building materials, auto parts and maintenance and other industries market operating rate will not exceed 10% .

Therefore, it is of the utmost importance to ensure an orderly and focused resumption of economic activity.

At present, the prevention and control of the epidemic situation is still the primary task. The circulation of commerce and service places are the main public spaces for people to gather and flow. With the increase in the number of people returning for the Spring Festival, the supply and demand of necessities in large and medium-sized cities will expand, the importance and urgency of speeding up the resumption of work in commercial and trade enterprises has been further highlighted. The overall consideration of mofcom in carrying out the resumption of production and operation is to guide local scientific assessment, classified management and control, highlighting key points and gradually expanding the scope on the premise of carrying out epidemic prevention and control measures.

That's wise. Don't Overdo it.
